ISSUE  -> Habits marked as "✓ Completed" would revert to "Done Today?" after reloading the page because the completion status was only stored in the frontend state.
CHANGE -> The application now retrieves today's completion status from the backend, updates the completed habits state, and correctly displays the button status based on data stored in the database.
